新臺幣一百萬元以下罰金。\r\n前五項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/ILDM/110%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c6%2c20211206%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"ILDM,110,訴,6,20211206,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"6","JDATE":"20211206","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}